                      <%= image_tag('diego.jpg', class: 'avatar rounded-circle') %></div>
                    <h6> Diego </h6>
                    <p class="text-muted"> As a dedicated dog dad, Diego took inspiration from his own Bestie, Sundae to create everything Bestie Life is today. </p>
                </div>


 <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4 text-center text-center__features">
