                      <%= image_tag('aparna.jpg', class: 'avatar rounded-circle') %></div>
                    <h6> Aparna </h6>
                    <p class="text-muted"> Bestie Life's official back end wiz, there aren't too many problems Aparna can't solve. </p>
                </div>

 <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4 text-center text-center__features">
                <div class="diego-feature">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4 text-center">

                      <%= image_tag('cheena.png', class: 'avatar rounded-circle') %></div>
                    <h6> Cheena </h6>
                    <p class="text-muted"> As a dog and cat mama, Cheena's besties always come first. Cheena loves bringing ideas to live </p>
